game.name: Princess Midnight Party
game.description:
These three beautiful Disney princesses are pretty excited to go on a midnight party today. They suddenly realize that their current outfits are not suitable for this occasion. The primary motto of these beauties now is to pick up the nice dresses for the midnight party. Your excellent fashion sense has attracted them to hire you as their personal stylist. Would you accept this job and guide them to attain the unmatched party looks? Join Princess Midnight Party game and help them to select the most fashionable outfits to rock!
The right side of the screen will show you outfit and other needful accessory options in this brand new dressing game. Click the princess who you want to dress up first and start mixing and matching as many options as you can until you create the awesome party look for her! Begin with the princess Ariel who wants a stylish hairstyle, a lovely matching goggle or a handbag, an elegant piece of party style outfit and a sparkling jewelry item! Then move to the Jasmine who loves to put on a short party dress combined with a matching pair of shoes and other accessories. 
Make sure to change the look of the third princess named Rapunzel who is also waiting for her turn. Click on her and explore all the dresses, hairstyles, pair of sandals, and other necessary items including jewelry, handbag or a goggle! Once you change the look of the three princesses, you can click the option given at the bottom to change the background. Hit the next button after making all the changes you like in this html5 princess dress up game for kids! It is our pleasure to serve you with the best dress-up games for girls that are playable online for free, no download required.
